         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne Botanic Garden ¶ 8th August 1867. ¶ Dear Sir, ¶  ¶ Having received last night at Queen'scliff ¶ Vic. ¶  ¶ your communication desiring me to undertake the superintendence and arrangements for...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">67.08.08</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To James Grant</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">P67/10542, unit 631, VPRS 44/P inward registered and unregistered correspondence, VA 538 Department of Crown Lands and Survey, Public Record Office, Victoria.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS is copy by unknown.</p>
               </note>Melbourne Botanic Garden</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">8th August 1867.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Dear Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Having received last night at Queen'scliff<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Vic.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>your communication desiring me to undertake the superintendence and arrangements for gravelling certain paths at Toorack<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>i.e. the Governor's residence.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and for effecting certain plantations at his Excellency's residence, I have at once returned to my Office though I am still extremely weak, as such work could not possibly be directed from a distance without much loss of time and inconvenience.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I beg at the earliest moment to bring under your cognisance that I have no financial means in my department for any additional work, that indeed I have not even funds to effect the remaining repairs of the damages caused by last year's flood, and for some other urgent work in my Department</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It will thus be necessary that a special sum should be provided for this work and I will do myself the honor to submit to you in about a day, an approximate estimate of the cost of the work, desired by you to be effected<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See M to J. Grant, 9 August 1867, in this edition as 67-08-09a.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I shall be happy whenever the needful funds are placed at my disposal to engage the workmen carts &amp;c and use my best discretion to carry out your wishes as far as it is within my power (means)</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>But when these arrangements shall have been effected, I must beg of you to concede me permission to return to a quiet place on the coast or to some other rural locality, to renew my chance of regaining health and strength, and I trust you will in your usual goodness not object to it, especially as I can remain in frequent communication with the Department and take with me material for official work</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Dear Mr Grant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your very regardful</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Signed F.M.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Hon. J. M Grant &amp;c &amp;c</p>
         </div>
